messages.messageBody:
Got an e-mail. GOOD!! Here, I'll share it:

Hey there!

Just wanted to drop a quick note to let you know what is going on.

The modem in my old computer is dead! It's a proprietary part so very
expensive to replace. I found a newer old computer, and paid only $20 at the
surplus place for the schools.

Anyway, if I can come up with $200 to have him get that one up and running
then I should be back online next week sometime. I'm really missing everyone!

Had my oral surgery on Thursday, still puffy and bruised but feeling a lot
better today.

Celebrated my Birthday yesterday and all is well.

Take care, I'll be back soon. :)

Love,

Ren
